Privacy Policy
Last updated: 2/10/24
Welcome to BaBa Stories!
BaBa Stories is a dedicated app providing kids with a wide array of bedtime stories in a safe and engaging environment. We prioritize the privacy and safety of our young users and their families. This Privacy Policy outlines our practices concerning the handling of any information.
Collection of Information
BaBa Stories does
not
collect any personal information, device IDs, or any other data from its users. Our app is designed to provide a safe, secure, and private experience without tracking or monitoring our users' activities.
Third-party Analytics:
We have intentionally designed our app without any third-party analytics. Our focus is solely on providing a safe and enjoyable experience for children, and we do not collect any data for analytical purposes.
Third-party Advertising:
Our app does not feature any third-party advertising. We are committed to maintaining an ad-free environment to ensure the safety and privacy of our young users.
Data Sharing with Third Parties:
At no point does our app share any data with third parties. We prioritize the confidentiality and security of all user information and interactions within the app, keeping them strictly within our ecosystem.
User or Device Data Collection:
Our app does not collect any user or device data for purposes beyond its core functionality. We have implemented stringent privacy measures to ensure that all interactions within the app remain confidential and are not transmitted externally.
Parental Gates
To further ensure the safety of our young users, BaBa Stories incorporates parental gates. These features require verification by adults for any external links or significant actions within the app, ensuring a controlled and safe environment for children to explore.
Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. Thus, we advise you to review this page periodically for any changes. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page. These changes are effective immediately, after they are posted on this page.
Contact Us
If you have any questions or suggestions about our Privacy Policy, do not hesitate to contact us at
contact@baba-stories.com